Automated feedback loop where results from experiments continuously inform future tests and hypotheses.
- Continuous Knowledge Expansion:

The system autonomously integrates new research data and results to continuously expand its knowledge base.
Real-time updating of hypotheses and experiment designs based on newly acquired knowledge.
- Collaboration & Real-Time Reporting:

A user interface for researchers to collaborate with the system monitor progress and provide input.
