(json 328 (description "To implement TrustLevel services on SingularityNET we must provide our API in gRPC, an open-source universal RPC framework. This milestone includes (1) the creation of the protocol buffers; (2) the server logic and code for the web server and gRPC server that can handle request for our TrustLevel services; (3) the code that creates a gRPC client that can call the &lsquo;Content quality&rsquo; method of our Trustlevel service."))
(json 328 (development_description ""))
