(json 528 (development_description "A comprehensive research report outlining findings including a feasibility assessment and risk analysis will serve as a crucial foundation for our project providing insights into the feasibility of integrating decentralized AI with IoT. Approval from the project lead and validation from external experts will ensure the credibility and accuracy of our findings. We have allocated 2000 for this milestone allowing sufficient resources for thorough research and analysis. The 2-month duration will provide ample time to conduct comprehensive research and produce a detailed feasibility study. Our comprehensive research report will include a feasibility assessment and risk analysis serving as the foundation for our project by providing insights into integrating decentralized AI with IoT. Preliminary market research will be part of this report assessing market needs and opportunities to guide our strategic direction. Additionally a detailed project backlog will outline tasks timelines and resource allocation for subsequent phases ensuring a structured and efficient project progression."))
